videos.description: Sagaba Konate reaches above the rim to block the shot from Baylor.
videos.headline: West Virginia's Konate rejects Baylor layup

videos.description: Mark Vital drives to the basket and lays it in between three West Virginia defenders.
videos.headline: Baylor breaks press with acrobatic layup

videos.description: Sagaba Konate grabs the ball straight off the backboard, leading to a corner 3-pointer from Chase Harler.
videos.headline: Huge block leads to West Virginia 3-pointer

videos.description: Jake Lindsey passes to Tyson Jolly in the paint who throws down the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Quick passing sets up Baylor dunk

videos.description: Sagaba Konate rejects another layup attempt from Baylor, grabbing the block off the backboard.
videos.headline: Konate pins another block to the backboard

videos.description: Jevon Carter hits the 3-pointer from the wing to break the tie with under a minute left in the game.
videos.headline: Carter knocks down clutch 3-pointer for West Virginia
